6. FITS I/O Interface
---------------------
None


7. Linear algebra module
------------------------
None


8. Model module
---------------
The diffuse map normalization for Monte Carlo simulations has been corrected in
GModelSpatialDiffuseMap::set_mc_cone() to properly account for the case that the
diffuse map has not been normalized. This fixes #1584.


